ain SM, Reinhold C, Mitchell DG. Cirrhosis and lesion characterization at MR imaging. <em>RadioGraphics</em> 2009;29(6):1637–1652.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.296095508">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19959512/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Cirrhosis+and+lesion+characterization+at+MR+imaging&amp;author=SM+Hussain&amp;author=C+Reinhold&amp;author=DG+Mitchell&amp;publication_year=2009&amp;journal=RadioGraphics&amp;pages=1637-1652&amp;doi=10.1148%2Frg.296095508&amp;pmid=19959512">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">41.</div><div id="r41" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Varela M, Sanchez W, Bruix J, Gores GJ. Hepatocellular carcinoma in the setting of liver transplantation. <em>Liver Transpl</em> 2006;12(7):1028–1036.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/lt.20833">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16799950/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Hepatocellular+carcinoma+in+the+setting+of+liver+transplantation&amp;author=M+Varela&amp;author=W+Sanchez&amp;author=J+Bruix&amp;author=GJ+Gores&amp;publication_year=2006&amp;journal=Liver+Transpl&amp;pages=1028-1036&amp;doi=10.1002%2Flt.20833&amp;pmid=16799950">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">42.</div><div id="r42" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Bruix J, Sherman M; American Association for the Study of Liver Diseases. Management of hepatocellular carcinoma: an update. <em>Hepatology</em> 2011;53(3):1020–1022.</di